videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence fumbles the ball on the handoff and Syracuse's Syrac Alton recovers.
videos.headline: Syracuse recovers Lawrence's fumble

videos.description: Clemson caps off a 60-yard drive with a one-yard touchdown run by Travis Etienne in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Clemson runs wildcat formation for TD

videos.description: Eric Dungey rushes one-yard to the end zone to put Syracuse on top.
videos.headline: Syracuse reclaims lead from Clemson

videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence gets shaken up after taking a hit from Syracuse's defense.
videos.headline: Lawrence shaken up after big hit

videos.description: Jamal Custis leaps for an athletic grab between Clemson defenders.
videos.headline: Custis comes up with big catch for Syracuse

videos.description: Chase Brice takes over as Clemson's quarterback after Trevor Lawrence exited the game following a hit from Syracuse.
videos.headline: Brice replaces injured QB Lawrence for Clemson

videos.description: Clemson backup QB Chase Brice is intercepted by Syracuse's Trill Williams in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Syracuse intercepts Clemson's Brice

videos.description: Clemson's Hunter Renfrow comes up big on a 28-yard pass from QB Chase Brice.
videos.headline: Renfrow makes acrobatic catch for Clemson

videos.description: Eric Dungey's pass is intercepted by Clemson's A.J. Terrell.
videos.headline: Clemson intercepts Syracuse

videos.description: Syracuse recovers Clemson's muffed punt at the Tigers' 10-yard line to start the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Clemson muffs punt, gives Syracuse ball

videos.description: Syracuse extends the lead over Clemson 23-13 with a one-yard score by QB Eric Dungey.
videos.headline: Dungey runs in TD for Syracuse

videos.description: Travis Etienne hauls in a 26-yard touchdown from Chace Brice to close the gap with Syracuse 23-20.
videos.headline: Etienne hauls in a 26-yard touchdown for Clemson

videos.description: Clemson caps off a 94-yard drive with a two-yard score from Travis Etienne to give Clemson the lead over Syracuse in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Etienne's TD puts Clemson on top

videos.description: Eric Dungey is sacked by Clemson's Xavier Thomas for a loss of eight yards in the final moments of the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Clemson sacks Syracuse QB

videos.description: Tigers fans storm the field to celebrate Clemson's 27-23 victory over Syracuse.
videos.headline: Clemson storms the field after defeating Syracuse

videos.description: Clemson freshman QB Chase Brice talks about replacing injured starter Trevor Lawrence and leading Clemson to a 27-23 win over Syracuse.
videos.headline: Brice not fazed entering game for injured Lawrence
